the world looks perfect ♪

00:14.648 --> 00:17.450
♪ Nothing to rearrange ♪

00:17.483 --> 00:20.386
♪ Sometimes you just
get a feeling ♪

00:20.420 --> 00:23.156
♪ Like you need
some kind of change ♪

00:24.658 --> 00:28.394
♪ No matter what the odds are
this time ♪

00:28.428 --> 00:30.564
♪ Nothing’s gonna stand
in my way ♪

00:30.597 --> 00:34.067
♪ This flame in my heart
and a long lost friend ♪

00:34.100 --> 00:37.671
♪ Gives every dark street
a light at the end ♪

00:39.405 --> 00:42.342
♪ Standing tall ♪
♪ Standing tall ♪

00:42.375 --> 00:46.146
♪ On the wings of my dream ♪
♪ Wings of my dream ♪

